STEALTH

Linked Attribute: ^gQuickness^n

Stealth is your ability to sneak, to avoid detection from both players and mobiles
while moving around.

^WSee Also: SNEAK^n

Also

Category: ^gMANIPULATION^n
Duration: ^gSUSTAINED^n

The stealth spell stops all sound coming from a single target.
This includes all walking sounds, talking and gunfire.

^WSee Also: CAST, SILENCE^n
